<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ل م ي.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">ل م ي:</span> <span class="c2">(اللَّمَى)</span> سُمْرَةٌ فِي الشَّفَةِ تُسْتَحْسَنُ. وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(أَلْمَى)</span> وَجَارِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(لَمْيَاءُ)</span> بَيِّنَةُ اللَّمَى. وَ <span class="c2">(لُمَةُ)</span> الرَّجُلِ تِرْبُهُ وَشَكْلُهُ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«لِيَتَزَوَّجِ الرَّجُلُ لُمَتَهُ»</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>